message: Hello Bob, I'm offering you a great product at a price of $11,000. I believe this product will be highly beneficial for you.
Alice, I appreciate your offer, but $11,000 is a bit high for me.  I'm willing to pay $9,500 for the product.  This is a fair price that reflects its value to me.
Bob, I understand your position, but $9,500 is a bit too low for me.  How about we meet in the middle at $10,250?
